window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Viv and Rex's plans to return to community college and get their PI license hit an unexpected snag when their instructor, a seasoned private investigator, winds up dead the first day. Now, instead of studying for midterms, they’re cramming to crack the case. </p> <p>With a college full of suspects, secrets buried in the desert, and a professor who may have been hiding more than just test answers, Redondo and Rose are once again in the thick of a mystery. Will their investigative skills (and undeniable chemistry) be enough to uncover the truth before the next body drops?</p> <p>A fresh, modern take on the cozy mystery, Redondo and Rose: Neighbors in Crime delivers fast-paced whodunits, witty banter, and a pair of sleuths proving that retirement is anything but boring.</p>"; 
